    public class BaseIndexedMap<Key,​Value>
extends BaseMap<Key,​Value>
implements java.lang.Iterable<Value>, Indexable<Value>
    A map that allows access to data by both index and key. Note that LinkedHashMap preserves the order of values in the map, but it does not allow indexing of the map.
